#: ../../source/kv_cache_management/lookup.rst:93
msgid ""
"The field ``lmcache_default_instance`` shows the instance ID, followed by"
" a tuple of ``(location, matched_prefix_length)`` indicating the cache "
"location within that instance and matched prefix length. ``event_id`` is "
"an identifier of the controller operation and can typically be ignored."
msgstr "字段 ``lmcache_default_instance`` 显示实例 ID，后面是一个元组 ``(location, matched_prefix_length)``，指示该实例内的缓存位置和匹配前缀长度。 ``event_id`` 是控制器操作的标识符，通常可以忽略。"


